name: David Wenzel at That's Entertainment for FCBD 2012

desc.html: Artist David Thorn Wenzel added a signature and sketch to a fan's book at That's Entertainment in Worcester, MA. Wenzel, surrounded by fans and his own work, appeared at the pop culture emporium as part of the Free Comic Book Day celebration there on May 5, 2012.

wiki.Credit:
I took this photo of Wenzel while we both were present at a public event.
